OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning.
OL,7,FMostly dry in the afternoon and though
OL,8,Frather cloudy, some brighter spells
OL,9,Fwill develop.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry start then cloud
OL,12,Fthickening to bring a little rain at
OL,13,Ftimes later in the evening. The east
OL,14,Fturning clearer again overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,17,Frain at times, though parts of the
OL,18,Feast coast will stay dry. Some heavier
OL,19,Frain later in the evening, with strong
OL,20,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
