OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday bright with sunny intervals
OL,7,Fand blustery showers. Cloudy with rain
OL,8,Fon Thursday, some heavy. Then brighter
OL,9,Fagain on Friday with sunny intervals
OL,10,Fand a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
